{"tid":2120314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國指控兩名中國黑客　曾竊取香港示威資料","createTime":"2020-07-22T15:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T15:52:53.000Z","uid":335434,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfafdd59976fde887589b00b040adeb71817572","tid":2120314,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"美國司法部起訴兩名中國黑客，指他們涉嫌為中國國安部竊取新冠病毒疫苗研究和香港示威者資料。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書指，兩人譯音分別是34歲的李嘯宇和33歲的董家志。<span class=\"red\"><strong>入侵對象包括一個香港示威者常用的英國通訊應用程式﹔香港一名社會運動組織者，以及兩名曾在香港支持民主運動的加拿大公民。他們的電郵亦被入侵。</strong></span>美國聯邦調查局已發出通緝令，相信他們目前在中國境內。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人表示，中國政府一貫反對並打擊任何形式的網絡攻擊和網絡犯罪，要求美方立即停止在網絡安全問題上對中方的污蔑抹黑。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539328-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539328-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=ab2c1963\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539328-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7df2a68d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539328-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"35c7ec2aa7153042eaf518b7884bc9814c8cd773","tid":2120314,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"英國通訊app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e5f2b468caa6c73b95211fc0297226892c4d33","tid":2120314,"uid":120913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35c7ec2aa7153042eaf518b7884bc9814c8cd773","tid":2120314,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy